
If you want to choose the data source in the inputs pass it as a parameter of the function <code>input</code>.<br />
You can choose any of the following as the default source:
* open;
* high;
* low;
* close;
* hl2;
* hlc3;
* ohlc4.


Example 1. Simple
<source>
study("My Script")
src = input(close)
plot(src)
</source>


Example 2. Extended
<source>
study("My Script")
src = input(title="Source", type=source, defval=close)
plot(src)
</source>
